<div id="main-wrapper">
	<main>
		<header>
			<h1>Website {{!-- <span>to</span> --}}to Chrome app</h1>
			<p>Generates <a href="https://developer.chrome.com/apps/about_apps">Chrome Apps</a> with a fullscreen <code>&lt;webview&gt;</code> of some url.</p>
			<p>That way, you can use web apps more easily.</p>
		</header>
		<a href="{{projectLink}}" id="github-logo">
		<svg viewBox="0 0 34 34" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
