		</p>
		<p>Open Source on <a id="githubLink" href="{{projectLink}}">GitHub</a>. Pls contribute if u want :)</p>
		<p>Made in the bedroom of <a href="{{authorLink}}">Matthias Vogt</a>.</p>
	</footer>

</div>


